                <h2 id="427" class="accordion-title section-427 is-active" role="tab" aria-expanded="true"><a href="#">Benefits/Harms of Implementing the Guideline Recommendations</a></h2>
            <div class="accordion-panel is-active" role="tabpanel">
                        <h3><a href="#">Potential Benefits</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Appropriate management and support of children and young people on the autism spectrum</p>
<p>See the "From Evidence to Recommendations" sections of the full version of the original guideline document for additional details about benefits of specific interventions.</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Potential Harms</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Side effects of medications</p>
<p>See the "From Evidence to Recommendations" sections and Chapter 9 in the full version of the original guideline document for additional details about potential harms of specific interventions.</p></div></p>

